title: Riot Kale
body: Once the Riot Kayle came out for the 10th anniversary, I never received it. I'm level 7 and I should have gotten it right? I also never got Kayle as a champion, either.

replies.body: Gifts are still be sent out to a lot of eligilbe accounts, so it's going to be a bit of time before everyone receives it.  We'll have updates through our [support banner](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/227317608--Sept-14-Anniversary-gifts-are-currently-being-distributed-You-may-not-receive-them-right-away-so-please-be-patient-).  Hang on until this is all done!
